'''Curovao''' was both one of the [[Brentaal Houses]] and one of the [[City/Legends|cities]] on [[Brentaal IV/Legends|Brentaal IV]]. The [[Curovao family]] was both noble and rich, and it founded the homonym city. In some [[Time/Legends|time]], the city of Curovao became one of the largest cities on Brentaal, and the family used it to control much of its business during the times of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Old Republic]].

